\f0\fs22 \\begin\{mmdef\}[Semantic mediator]\\label\{def:semantic-mediator\}\
The semantic mediator pattern encapsulates differences in semantic representations, promotes semantic loose coupling and enables to vary conversations in response to changes in business collaborations. By doing so, it trades the complexity of the conversations and the underlying agent interactions / data exchange with the complexity of the mediator.\
\\end\{mmdef\}  \
